Wonka Chocolate Machine Firmware Requirements
---------------------------------------------
1. Define the purpose of the application.
   a. Create firmware to drive the Wonka Chocolate machine and handle order selection,
      cash collection, creation of the bars and handling for lack of raw materials.
2. Define the logical steps of the firmware.
   a. Create the data dictionaries for CHOCOLATE_CHOICES and raw_materials.
   b. Create a total_money_collected var and init to 0.
   c. Create a SHUTDOWN_PASSWORD and init to '8675309'.
   d. Create has_raw_materials function to check if there are enough raw materials 
      in the machine.
   e. Create a collect_money function to collect money into the machine.
   f. Create a has_enough_money function to check to see if customer put in
      enough money into the machine.
   g. Crete a bake_chocolate_bar function to bake chocolate bar from raw
      materials.
   h. Create a stats function to show machine statistics.
   i. Create a machine_active var and init to True.
   j. Create a choices list and add 'dark', 'caramel', 'mint', 'surprise',
      'stats', and 'shutdown'.
   k. Create main while loop to account for machine_active.  Handle input.  
      Handle shutdown.  Handle stats.  Handle if valid choice.
